features: Designed To Perform – Equip your kitchen with the right cookware to bring you long lasting performance and quality food results the healthy way. Our Fry Pan features a 3-layer coating engineered in Germany from stone-derived shield technology. The protective coating significantly extends the life cycle of the frying pan while the ultra-durable aluminum construction and magnetic base provide optimal heat conduction. With these features, you won’t look at other cookware in the same way!

Non-Stick and Even Heat Distribution – Reinforced coating provides unprecedented non-stick cooking performance for easy food release, easy clean up, and better browning and searing. With excellent heat conduction, heat is evenly distributed across the whole nonstick pan, cooking foods faster to save you time. Only low to medium heat is required, keeping your cooking energy-friendly!

Safe Cooking – No more nasty hidden chemicals with this healthy and eco-friendly alternative to classic frying pans non-stick. Our specialized coating is corrosion resistant and free of APEO, PFOA, PFOS, PFAS, PFBS, GenX, and other lesser-known health-harmful chemicals, such as NEP and NMP. Great for busy families to keep meals as healthy and toxin-free as possible.

Cool-To-The-Touch – The pan’s versatile deep shape, light weight, and stylish ergonomic handle make this pan for cooking ideal for everyday use. The EverCool stainless steel handle remains cool-to-touch during the busiest of stovetop cooking. Oven safe and suitable for use on all cook tops, including induction. Practical as an egg pan or for gourmet dishes, either way this non-stick fry pan is the perfect way to make magic happen in the kitchen!

Superior Quality With Mueller - We are here to offer you only the best quality products designed to make your life easier. If you need any help, please feel free to contact us. Our unparalleled 24/7 live telephone customer support is ready and waiting to assist with anything you need!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: SUPERIOR QUALITY NON-TOXIC FRY PANS Enjoy preparation of your meals with Mueller HealthyStone Frying Pans – available in 3 different sizes and 2 color options to best suit your cookware needs. These frying pans features a unique German-engineered, 3-layer coating from stone-derived shield technology – properties that elevate cooking performance without any toxic or harsh chemicals.

FRUSTRATION-FREE COOKING Mueller’s fry pan offers performance where it matters. With excellent heat conduction through the heavy-duty aluminum core, heat will be evenly distributed across the whole frying pan. Enjoy evenly cooked meals and energy savings from only having to use low to medium heat. NON-STICK PERFORMANCE No more food sticking to your pan. Mueller’s non-stick reinforced coating allows for easy food release, making cooking easier and healthier too with less oil required. The coating makes clean-up effortless, plus its dishwasher safe for added convenience. NATURAL & SAFE COATING The natural elements of the stone-derived layers mean there is absolutely no exposure to toxic substances such as APEO, PFOA, PFOS, PFBS, GenX fluorinated chemicals, and the lesser-known chemicals NMP and NEP commonly found in other cookware.

The versatile deep shape design makes the pan ideal for everyday cooking. The hardened coating doesn’t scratch like other non-stick pans and the cool-to-the-touch stainless steel handle provides comfort and ease while cooking on any cooktop, including induction. Oven safe to 450°F. Makes cooking meals easier than ever.

HEALTHY COATING Pure and natural coating free of nasty chemicals for healthier and cleaner cooking. SAVE ON ENERGY Quick heating so no time or electrical energy is wasted. SAVE ON WATER Cleaning is as easy as a simple rinse and wipe. STONE-DERIVED NONSTICK Relying on nature’s strongest properties to ensure long-lasting performance.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this pan
reviews.reviewText: Use this pan all the time. Hold heats evenly and cooks great. Cleaning is a breeze. I only use it a medium to low temps, and only with wooden utensils. Haven’t had any issues with it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I had been wanting to try a stone pan for a while, were they really non-stick? This is now my favorite pan. It is remarkable for heat distribution and being non-stick. It is true, your food just slides right off. And super easy to clean up. I've used it for breakfast, lunch and dinner and it performs great. Gets me in and out of the kitchen quickly. May save up my pennies and get one in a larger size.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I have been using this pan about four times a week for six months. I handwash it and I am careful to use wooden spoons only. The pan is nonstick to this day, very easy to heat, and all around a very good buy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This pan is very durable, and scratch resistant. Also it has thick bottom which is greatfor cooking and not stick surface. I enjoy to use it for cooking, but only thing that I don’t like is that it turned yellow, even I was careful and didn’t use very high heat while I was cooking. Overall, great purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 2 months of use and its great.
reviews.reviewText: So, my wife is 'cast iron club' and didn't really want to get another pan. We are vegetarian, however, and use a lot of protein replacing products. They often stick really well to cast iron and are a pain to get off. (yes, it is seasoned well).So, because I didn't want to spend 10 min cleaning the cast iron after every egg, I bought this. The coating is amazing. With just a little butter or oil, nothing sticks to it. There is one problem, and its me, so I'm not taking a star off. The bottom/edges of our pan are already gross with grease. The inside cleans up very easily, but the edges don't seem to want to get clean. Even with baking soda and a gentle brush, or vinegar, I can't get them back to the original color. So, its not a showpiece pan, but it is a workhorse.We only use silicone utensils with it, so hopefully the coating will last. I know these do wear out after a couple years.TL:DR, this will make you not hate cooking eggs again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Finally the perfect pan for everyday use!
reviews.reviewText: After using this for several weeks it has become my favorite pan. Like the instructions say you only need to use low to medium heat and it cooks perfectly. The heat distribution is excellent and everything just slides off when your done cooking. I even stopped using oil when frying my salmon.
